{"tid":1641512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[電競戰線]懲罰完藍暴雪，係時候獎勵一個支持香港人既韓國平台","createTime":"2019-10-09T11:02:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T13:13:02.000Z","uid":137639,"like":79,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"044a58c9f7d91a9f3861ad2a3e80737b605e16bb","tid":1641512,"uid":137639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:02:42.000Z","msg":"個平台就係AfreecaTV！係香港預賽同之後既亞洲交流賽入面，我都戴左full gear同舉光復香港，時代革命既標語。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sw20urK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsw20urK.png&h=1310c837&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1VXS4Z5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1VXS4Z5.jpg&h=5a6adad2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而係有同admin溝通既情況之下主辦單位，即係AfreecaTV，係冇cut走我個cam同冇阻止我作政治表態<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且台灣既AfreecaTV之前都成日用岩岩被暴雪禁殺既賽評偷米<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cSFEK1G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcSFEK1G.png&h=68d60904&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人係時候用行動鼓勵吓依個韓國既直播平台，要比佢地知佢地冇做錯到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全部人開個Afreeca account follow香港同台灣afreeca既爐石channel<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Facebook比個like佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n知你班香港人懶，link都擺埋係度，禁兩個制難唔到你地既<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/AfreecaTVinHK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FAfreecaTVinHK%2F&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNsFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=3f7bc987\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/AfreecaTVinHK/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/AfreecaTV.Taiwan/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FAfreecaTV.Taiwan%2F&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNsFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=d546ef28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/AfreecaTV.Taiwan/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://play.afreecatv.com/atvtwhs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fplay.afreecatv.com%2Fatvtwhs&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNsFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=bbe3d7cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://play.afreecatv.com/atvtwhs</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://bj.afreecatv.com/atvhkhs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbj.afreecatv.com%2Fatvhkhs&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNsFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=b411b73a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bj.afreecatv.com/atvhkhs</a><br />\n<br />\n一定要大大力獎勵佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">食屎啦暴雪</span>"},{"pid":"d851d51191682eb3fc739dff12e8149de19c3011","tid":1641512,"uid":137639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:03:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d2c0c2c04f6ec49fb3fdace3401a83c32bfd1dcd","tid":1641512,"uid":258696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:04:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">國際戰線要人!！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">呢排國際上發生左幾單重要打<br />\nNBA、south park 、暴雪、red bull <br />\n大家點可以呢個時候懶！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>係時候要世界明白中國有幾醜惡!</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">國際戰線！全球抗共！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n任務：<br />\n1. Twitter 戰線 請用Tg入面既Twitter help<br />\n2 YouTube 英文短片<br />\n3. Reddit戰線</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">我地只有令全世界明白香港係幫自由世紀抵擋邪惡國家既先鋒，先可以令世人支持我地！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"695e0b2a6a861df418126f769b24fbb6111a37d9","tid":1641512,"uid":263213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:05:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f09799892674d37c915a3426e3befd1a153725cc","tid":1641512,"uid":137639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:11:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7ce7b03ed9d0dfe9735ee538556b74b516fa5281","tid":1641512,"uid":137639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:11:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"75c89b7ed7f61c36f8a094c7b37b5e7c92df4762","tid":1641512,"uid":137639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:11:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0373e35b6829a8606ce33950255e3380c13ea227","tid":1641512,"uid":137639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:12:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"17a075e56ef32633c7361174cba23303dfd52cf3","tid":1641512,"uid":137639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:12:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9eb25ff4694195e0606285ac4b1c6e7586cc0bb2","tid":1641512,"uid":137639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:12:55.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ca51ff4b6b50aa04750773ec475461737936ab76","tid":1641512,"uid":137639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:13:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d8f88c022b364e547caef10d91b95abb0392e41","tid":1641512,"uid":281972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c